spec_data.Name: perl-Devel-Hide
spec_data.Description:
Given a list of Perl modules/filenames, this module makes require and
use statements fail (no matter the specified files/modules are
installed or not).
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Fri 28 Jul 2017 10:53:40 AM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: Forces the unavailability of specified Perl modules (for testing)
